I agree with the feedback, thank you @drpngx and @martinwicke! This PR has been revised as follows:
- `tf.learn` -> `Estimator` under `learn.estimators` and `layers.feature_column`.
- `tf.learn.DataFrame` -> `DataFrame` under `learn.dataframe`.
- `tf.learn/inflow` -> `inflow` under installation shell scripts.
I would like you to review again this version.
